困列车，食物短缺… 《每日经济新闻》记者对求助信息进行大量求证，在拨打超过20个求助信息的电话后，发现在这些网上发布的求助信息所附的手机号绝大多数都无法接通，要么处于关机状态，要么是忙音。 同时，在接通的电话里，仍有人持续被困。其中，有的人接过十几个电话询问基本情况，还在等待救援；也有人手机就要没电，不知道具体的求助渠道和方式；还有人在K1628的列车上，信号时断时续… 原文链接：雨困郑州，打不通的电话成救援拦路虎 | 每日经济新闻"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2+Sd4MajpNA1EAMaCDY3NTY5OTM2IJ6d4IcGMAw4sgZAJnIJNDczODA1MzM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-26ac5e96c2bf6c0e67d486f07510e641_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1627186090.3677135","card_id":"Q_473754437","target":{"id":473754437,"title":"如何评价《原神》宵宫的传说任务？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/473754437","type":"question","created":1626855597,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":94,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,105508,406546],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I2+Sd4MajpNA1EAMaCDY3NTU4NTcyIK2x34cGMAQ4XkAncgk0NzM3NTQ0Mzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"42 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9514fae2ce719659b3f4152449f9f3a7_720w.jpg?source=2044ae36"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1627186090.3681822","card_id":"Q_474264183","target":{"id":474264183,"title":"德媒发文称「郑州洪水，没有任何排水系统能应对」，反映了哪些问题？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/474264183","type":"question","created":1627029320,"answer_count":308,"follower_count":1338,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1595,3853,18153,22846,751257],"comment_count":115,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"河南郑州等地近日遭遇连续强降雨，引发市区严重内涝让人揪心，事件引起全球关注。 《德国之声》中文网22日发布一篇题为“德国专家：郑州洪水‘没有任何排水系统能应对’”的文章，罕见地说了句公道话。报道称，德国锡根大学的洪涝专家严森（Jürgen Jensen）教授在得知郑州的最大小时降雨量达20